@prefix narr: <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#> .
@prefix xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#> .

GRAPH <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Digest_Narrative_1> {
  <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Digest_Narrative_1> a narr:Digest ;
    narr:digestOf <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_1> ;
    narr:childCount "5"^^xsd:integer ;
    narr:generatedFrom "8ca78317c58539e7b6c396994b6bb11ae44c1b3d" ;
    narr:narration """The origin of this architecture is anchored in the 2012 study of flocking-particle systems, where [narrative operates like a velocity or acceleration vector](narr:StyleObs_2) in collective behavior. This foundational metaphor has evolved into a [strategic-alignment assessment](narr:RubricAssess_StrategicAlignment) that treats narrative as the primary directional vector for AI meaning, rather than a secondary verification layer. The technical implementation moves away from boolean fact-checking toward [evidence accumulation via RDF named graphs](narr:Narrative_2), enabling nuanced weighting of content. Operationalizing this requires a [document registry](narr:Position_7) that manages audience, domain-specific drift thresholds, and evaluation criteria. However, the system faces significant friction: [one-shot generation quality is insufficient](narr:Position_1) for complex documents, necessitating expensive, multi-stage compilation cycles. The current trajectory emphasizes this shift from a verification tool to a knowledge growth driver, though the tension between the foundational reframe and actual system behavior remains a persistent, unresolved theme.""" ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_2> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Position_1> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Position_7> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#RubricAssess_StrategicAlignment> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_2> ;
    narr:keyPhrase [ narr:text "narrative operates like a velocity or acceleration vector in these particle systems" ; narr:phraseSource <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_2> ] ;
    narr:keyPhrase [ narr:text "Review is evidence accumulation via RDF named graphs, not a boolean state transition" ; narr:phraseSource <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_2> ] ;
    narr:keyPhrase [ narr:text "one-shot quality is insufficient for real documents" ; narr:phraseSource <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Position_1> ] ;
    narr:keyPhrase [ narr:text "knowledge growth driver, not just a verification tool" ; narr:phraseSource <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_2> ] ;
    narr:variation [ narr:text "The belief-vs-action gap: the foundational reframe is established, but system behavior has not yet fully aligned." ; narr:over <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_2> ] ;
    narr:variation [ narr:text "Economic constraint: the high cost of full-compile generation challenges the viability of the current one-shot production model." ; narr:over <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Position_1> ] ;
    narr:writer "google/gemini-3.1-flash-lite" .
}